data.description: This Newer Construction 4 bed, 2.5 bath two story home can be yours! Your new Home sits near the corner of the block! There's no neighbors behind, so privacy galore. The open floor plan is perfect for entertaining, and working from home. The Kitchen features a center island, stone counters, 42” wall cabinets, large pantry, and stainless-steel appliances. The Great room exudes radiant light throughout the main level.  There's a formal living room/office & a dining room along with upgraded high-grade flooring on the main level. The primary bedroom suite features a walk-in closet, separate shower, large soaking tub & double vanity. There's main floor laundry, upgraded lighting, spindled staircases from the second floor to the basement & Arch panel doors throughout. The lower level includes a bath rough-in & Sump pump. All items in the home are negotiable for sale. Come see your Dream Home Today! The neighborhood features easy access to Hwy 40/61, I-70 & shopping near Wentzville Parkway!
